high_descs: Walk straight towards the door and turn left towards the black table on your right.
Pick up the watch on the right side of the table.
Turn around to face the dining table.
Place the watch on the white plate to the left of the book.
Pick up the plate with the watch from the table.
Turn right, take a step forward, and then turn right to face the black table.
Place the plate to the left of the tissue box.
anns.task_desc: Place the watch on the table on a white plate.

high_descs: Walk forward, cross the room, turn left. Walk forward, turn right to face the black table along the wall.
Pick up the watch on the right side of the table.
Turn around to face the glass table.
Place the watch on the white plate to the left of the painting.
Pick up the watch and plate on the table.
Turn around to face the black table.
Place the plate and watch on the black table to the left of the tissue box.
anns.task_desc: Place a watch and a plate on the black table.

high_descs: Walk across the room to the black table against the wall.
Pick up the watch from the table.
Turn around and approach the rectangular table.
Place the watch on a white plate on the table.
Pick up the white plate on the table.
Turn around and approach the black table.
Place the plate on the left side of the black table.
anns.task_desc: Place a plate with a watch on it on the black table.
